{"tid":1945605,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"巴裔手足還押接近4個月後准予保釋","createTime":"2020-03-27T07:33:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-27T07:45:47.000Z","uid":240362,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"317cd27ad5339fd46c0678a4ab934c4a80dfed7e","tid":1945605,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T07:33:33.000Z","msg":"#觀塘裁判法院第七庭 #何俊堯裁判官 <br />\n#1209旺角 #判刑<br />\n<br />\n巴裔手足(18) ‼️已還押104天<br />\n襲擊致造成身體傷害（私了陳大鵬）<br />\n<br />\n3月13日在 #羅德泉主任裁判官 面前認罪，5封求情信包括家長、校長、社工，指出被告勇於改過及樂於助人，案件押後兩星期以等候背景、感化、教導所及心理報告，期間繼續還押<br />\n<br />\n被告已被還押接近4個月<br />\n<br />\n已索取背景、感化官及心理報告，背景報告指被告後悔行為，深切反省自己過失；感化官報告建議被告判處監禁或教導所；懲教署心理報告顯示被告需要行為指導，辯方希望判處感化，讓被告接受長時間指導<br />\n<br />\n辯方指出陳大鵬傷勢雖嚴重，惟被告對陳大鵬施加的傷害少，在事件中參與少<br />\n<br />\n案件押後至5月22日東區裁判法院第七庭，以索取另一份感化官及外間心理報告<br />\n<br />\n✅期間保釋批准✅<br />\n保釋條件如下：<br />\n擔保金5000<br />\n每週報到1次<br />\n<br />\nSOURCE: 法庭文字直播台 <a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live&d=UCgs38VSsqZrRa6JqpzgNopVoCVS%2BR9CeaLj%2Fs3YFXo%3D&h=ae5517cc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live</a>"},{"pid":"ea63d17c4b49961883b94a1650837e01e2f3e0f3","tid":1945605,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T07:40:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2225e8836a973193304d42a940f58f5aa4765b55","tid":1945605,"uid":263213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T07:42:00.000Z","msg":"手足辛苦你啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /